*   [calc (sam-programs) (‚≠ê5)](https://github.com/Sam-programs/zsh-calc) - Allows you to run math calculations with no prefixes.
*   [kubecolor (devopstales) (‚≠ê7)](https://github.com/devopstales/zsh-kubecolor) - Adds aliases for the `kubecolor` command.
*   [kubeconfig-mgr (‚≠ê7)](https://github.com/yhlooo/zsh-kubeconfig-mgr) - Makes managing multiple kubeconfig files easier.

*   [niotna (‚≠ê3)](https://github.com/niotna/niotna-theme) - Includes decorators for `git` status and current directory. Customizable colors.
